<br>
This Saturday the 19th at 8:00 pm EST I would like to invite all MacLears young and old to Lake Rathe for a Language skills event. Some of the languages on hand will be Elvish, Dark speech, TerDal, Dwarvish, and Barbarian a language all MacLears should speak.<br>
<br>
Bring Ale and food. Bring gear to swap or trade. Have a story or two on hand as well to swap while we train our skills.<br>
<br>
After there will be some festivities in the Arena. So those who have pets bring em. It will be a type of MacLear best of the best contest.<br>
<br>
Alternatively depending on attendance we can teach the cyclops and giants of the rathe mountains a thing or two after.<br>
<br>
Ravnanger<br>
Shaman of MacLear<br>
<br>
