Failte Brother Ravnanger,<br>
<br>
I have read of your event and I believe it will be a fine time!  I shall be there and will bring food as you have requested.  Additionally, the GuildMagic scrolls hold information on the languages I have learned during my travels.  <br>
<br>
If you wish me to teach or assist in training of a new language, I shall be happy to oblige.  One language, though, I will not be able to teach.  Thieves Cant, the language of our rogues, is one language that I swore I would not impart to others.  The rogue that imparted this tongue to me has sworn me to not teach it to others... and you know that I am bound by my word of honor.<br>
